		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yes, but I guess he meant another point: we do not use 50Hz electronics, as designed for european countries, PAL. Instead, things are released in NTSC <strong>or</strong> "near enough that like you explained before", hehe ^_^;; The same is valid for games: there's no PAL games, they would be unplayable here, unless a transcoder device is used, of course (sort of).

		

